text: Eisner or Eissner may refer to: * Eisner (surname), including a list of people with the name * Eisner Loboa (born 1987), Colombian-born Mexican footballer * , several United States Navy ships * Eisner Peak, Graham Land, Antarctica * Eisner Award, annual awards for achievement in comics * Eisner Food Stores, a chain of supermarkets in Illinois and Indiana from 1901 to 1981 == See also == * William F. Eisner Museum of Advertising & Design, a museum in Milwaukee, Wisconsin
